  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Factoring out the coefficient <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one third\"></span>, the given expression can be rewritten as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one third times, open parenthesis, x squared, minus 6, close parenthesis\"></span>. The expression <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x squared, minus 6\"></span> can be approached as a difference of squares and rewritten as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, x minus the square root of 6, close parenthesis, times, open parenthesis, x plus the square root of 6, close parenthesis\"></span>. Therefore, <span class=\"italic\">k</span> must be <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the square root of 6\"></span>.<p>Choice A is incorrect. If <span class=\"italic\">k</span> were 2, then the expression given would be rewritten as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one third times, open parenthesis, x minus 2, close parenthesis, times, open parenthesis, x plus 2, close parenthesis\"></span>, which is equivalent to <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one third, x squared, minus four thirds\"></span>, not <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one third, x squared, minus 2\"></span>.</p><p>Choice B is incorrect. This may result from incorrectly factoring the expression and findin